oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: If That's The Only Way - Johnny Duncan and June Stearns performance; Back To Back (We're Strangers) - Johnny Duncan and June Stearns performance
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of If That's The Only Way, written by Ben Peters, published by Shelby Singleton Music Inc., produced by Frank Jones, recorded in December 1968 at Columbia Recording Studio in Nashville, TN, released by Columbia on January 21, 1969, and performed by Johnny Duncan and June Stearns. Performance of Back To Back (We're Strangers), written by Marian Francis, produced by Frank Jones, recorded in December 1968, at Columbia Recording Studio in Nashville, TN, released by Columbia on January 21, 1969, and performed by Johnny Duncan and June Stearns.
